  "prompt": "How can I arrange a personal counselling session with Tanmoy Ray?",
  "response": "To arrange a personal counselling session with Tanmoy Ray, you can follow these general steps:\n\n1. **Contact Information**: Look for Tanmoy Ray\u2019s official website or professional social media profiles to find contact details.\n\n2. **Schedule an Appointment**: Many professionals have a scheduling system or an appointment book. Check if there is an online booking option or if you need to call or email.\n\n3. **Provide Necessary Information**: When reaching out, be prepared to provide your name, contact information, and any specific issues or topics you'd like to address in the session.\n\n4. **Confirm Availability and Fees**: Make sure to verify the availability for the session and inquire about fees or payment methods.\n\n5. **Follow Up**: If you don\u2019t receive a response within a few days, consider following up to confirm your request.\n\nIf you can't find direct contact information, consider searching for counseling directories or platforms that might list available professionals, including Tanmoy Ray.",
